{
  "page": "Pussywillows",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Pussywillows</b> was a brothel during the reigns of kings <a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Daeron II Targaryen\">Daeron II</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys I Targaryen\">Aerys I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Its location is unknown.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pussywillows&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Pussywillows was the place where <a href=\"/index.php/Penny_Jenny\" title=\"Penny Jenny\">Penny Jenny</a> came to live and work after the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Redgrass_Field\" title=\"Battle of the Redgrass Field\">Battle of the Redgrass Field</a>. There she raised her son, <a href=\"/index.php/Glendon_Flowers\" title=\"Glendon Flowers\">Glendon Flowers</a>, and her daughter. It was within the establishment that Glendon was eventually <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knighted</a> by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Morgan_Dunstable\" title=\"Morgan Dunstable\">Morgan Dunstable</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Glendon described Pussywillows as an inn to Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a>, when mentioning where he had grown up, in order to prevent having to admit he had grown up in a brothel.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pussywillows&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Given that Jenny, a prostitute working at the brothel, is known to have died in the riverlands, the Pussywillows is likely located somewhere in the riverlands.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pussywillows&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Mystery_Knight\" title=\"The Mystery Knight\">The Mystery Knight</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404203230\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.013 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.014 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 211/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8690/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 733/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 28/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1645/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    9.093      1 -total\n 61.75%    5.615      3 Template:Ref\n 33.62%    3.057      3 Template:Ref/core\n 24.46%    2.224      2 Template:References\n 21.77%    1.979      1 Template:Notes\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:4686-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404203230 and revision id 261274\n -->\n",
